    "summary": "AN ACT TO PROHIBIT RETAIL FOOD ESTABLISHMENTS FROM IMPOSING COST-PLUS PRICING FORMULAS WITHOUT PUBLICLY POSTING NOTICE OF THE COST-PLUS PRICING FORMULA; TO PROVIDE A PENALTY FOR THE CRIME; TO PROVIDE THAT A VIOLATION OF THE SECTION SHALL CONSTITUTE AN UNLAWFUL TRADE PRACTICE; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
